    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="C4 PTR Menu Overview" class="article-title">
          C4 PTR Menu Overview
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2026-06-02T17:51:55Z" title="2026-06-02T17:51:55Z" data-datetime="relative">June 02, 2026 17:51</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/52244580822419-C4-PTR-Menu-Overview/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>The C4 PTR map gives you access to several menus that help you manage your fleets, inventory, crew, crafting jobs, scans, buildings, and galaxy view.</p><p>This article gives a quick overview of the main menus available from the map screen.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JR5SQVWYEYNT5H439P0FC">Top menu bar</h2><p>The top menu bar is visible from the main map.</p><p>It includes the following menus:</p><ul><li class="wysiwyg-list-bold" data-list-item-id="e70f1eb0c3b68691cd9eea3f87049ed23"><strong>My Fleets</strong></li><li class="wysiwyg-list-bold" data-list-item-id="e9f010f1a94b6188ff165a444a7825e99"><strong>Inventory</strong></li><li class="wysiwyg-list-bold" data-list-item-id="e1f027791b4407c16e9e5bc250ca26b36"><strong>Crew</strong></li><li class="wysiwyg-list-bold" data-list-item-id="e70bf550493b7ab74366a5066d3eee2c0"><strong>Crafting</strong></li><li class="wysiwyg-list-bold" data-list-item-id="e1eca1c0bae89653046a60811cbedbe4f"><strong>Scans</strong></li><li class="wysiwyg-list-bold" data-list-item-id="ebe2c81c2f2f0828efd64b72fd9c129d6"><strong>Buildings</strong></li><li class="wysiwyg-list-bold" data-list-item-id="e1151db8578f71d7c4e9892828df7bcd1"><strong>Galaxy</strong></li></ul><p>Each menu gives you a different way to view or manage your activity across the galaxy.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 803/113;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244542477587" width="803" height="113"></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JRAPCRRHC6AEA7HBF55MC">My Fleets</h2><p>The <strong>My Fleets</strong> menu lets you select your fleets without needing to manually find them on the map.</p><p>From this menu, you can click one of your fleets to select it. Once selected, you can use the fleet action bar to perform available actions.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 975/935;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244542478355" width="975" height="935"></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JRFM5SF8S313XFQTPMPNA">Inventory</h2><p>The <strong>My Inventory</strong> menu gives you an overview of your inventory across the galaxy.</p><p>You can use it to see where your inventory, crew, and ships are located.</p><p>Clicking a base from this menu will focus that base on the map and allow you to enter the Starbase directly.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 940/1044;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244580807059" width="940" height="1044"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JRR55SXQ2Y8EK0VBV11V1">Crew</h2><p>The <strong>My Crew</strong> menu shows where your crew members are stationed.</p><p>It shows crew assigned to fleets as well as crew located at Starbases.</p><p>Clicking a base from this menu will focus that base on the map and allow you to enter the Starbase directly.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 950/725;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244580807699" width="950" height="725"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JRWK7X2ZV15NAYE9KEB36">Crafting</h2><p>The <strong>My Crafting Efforts</strong> menu gives you an overview of crafting jobs currently processing across the galaxy.</p><p>Completed crafting jobs cannot be collected from this menu.</p><p>To collect completed crafting jobs, you must go to the Starbase where the crafting is being processed.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 931/840;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244542480915" width="931" height="840"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JS0ZHJP94P6BQ3B6N6RZG">Scans</h2><p>The <strong>My Scans</strong> menu gives you an overview of fleets that are ready to scan or have already scanned and are currently on scanning cooldown.</p><p>Use this menu to quickly check which fleets are available for scanning activity.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 993/851;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244542482195" width="993" height="851"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JS5G1B089EMDFNXJ05CY4">Buildings</h2><p>The <strong>My Buildings</strong> menu gives you an overview of buildings you have constructed.</p><p>This menu includes two tabs:</p><ul><li class="wysiwyg-list-bold" data-list-item-id="e0d33742028ee25d1507a5cef69c004f7"><strong>Claim Stakes</strong></li><li class="wysiwyg-list-bold" data-list-item-id="eb379ebd9ce38d8e3d61a7f2db01c8df0"><strong>Crafting Habs</strong></li></ul><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 977/929;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244542482963" width="977" height="929"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JSERW18A0VEFYZ84C5GQZ">Galaxy</h2><p>The <strong>My Galaxy</strong> menu gives you an overview of systems in the galaxy.</p><p>You can save planets from this menu to favorite them. Favorited planets are pinned to the top of the list, making them easier to access later.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 959/874;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244542484499" width="959" height="874"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JSK8WP7K0ZSG0FGPFEXEH">Player menu</h2><p>The player menu is located in the top-right corner of the screen.</p><p>This area shows your character name, current level, and several additional icons.</p><p>From this area, you can access other menus such as:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id="ec8b467dc0457f48ea6230e422ab86aad">Leaderboards</li><li data-list-item-id="e09843ec4dfa10e71dd384909a61a1464">Council Rank</li><li data-list-item-id="e6584a1f8f42f0a82c2bd22acb2b6a002">Marketplace</li><li data-list-item-id="e1a0b442e22687cb29e5568dc61685783">Community feedback and bug reporting</li><li data-list-item-id="ed397d25a172fbb40a0e6755a113993c1">Notifications</li><li data-list-item-id="e5ae12f0aacbceb7ce604199bf5187afa">Game and account settings</li></ul><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 787/118;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244542484883" width="787" height="118"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JSRKR5YVXBVRJMASJS3Y4">Leaderboards</h2><p>Clicking the leaderboard text near your character name opens the leaderboard menu.</p><p>Leaderboards may not be active during the current PTR. When leaderboards are live, this is where leaderboard-specific information will be available.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 593/1017;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244580814227" width="593" height="1017"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JSWZW8DF6EX1DJWNVH5RR">&nbsp;Council Rank</h2><p>The <strong>Council Rank</strong> menu is where you spend skill points to unlock research nodes.</p><p>Many actions in C4 PTR require research before you can progress deeper into a career or gameplay path.</p><p>During PTR, players may be able to use <strong>God Mode</strong> to avoid basic research requirement restrictions. This node is located at the top of the Council Rank tree.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 2174/1549;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244580814867" width="2174" height="1549"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JT153Q0SA3J35M2H12V65">Marketplace</h2><p>The marketplace can be used to buy and sell resources with other players within your faction.</p><p>The marketplace is still early in development during PTR, so its features and behavior may change over time.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JTY7SWBXCQFATKS9SBR6F">Community feedback and bug reporting</h2><p>Clicking the orange bug icon opens the support menu.</p><p>From this menu, you can access:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id="ed7fb4dfa3e926d9bb64523870eeaa825">The Knowledge Base</li><li data-list-item-id="ee69ac0be01c1c9f22c4f0e9622050e25">The Community Reports Dashboard</li><li data-list-item-id="e380619c7a3be3375c95849d2b004d2f3">Bug reporting</li><li data-list-item-id="e52cf7861c69acbcdfadffe81c72b541a">Feedback and suggestions</li><li data-list-item-id="e6cb641845485c5a9d8c0fb40c5a5784a">Feature requests</li><li data-list-item-id="ea15f69eb839c2cb62a983d3c57b73795">Support ticket creation</li></ul><p>If you encounter an issue or have feedback, use this menu so the team can review it properly.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 1383/642;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244580816147" width="1383" height="642"></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JV37Y75NX1ZJDHSG3C9Q1">Notifications</h2><p>The notifications menu works as a transaction log.</p><p>Successful and failed transactions will appear there.</p><p>If you think a transaction failed or did not process correctly, this should be one of the first places you check.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 784/828;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244580816787" width="784" height="828"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JV76HWGZAZN0FMNPA7W9J">Game and account settings</h2><p>The settings menu contains account and game options, including:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id="ece63310ae5753f72ba80d854fd3b2665"><strong>Account Settings</strong> - View wallet balances and your daily check-in streak.</li><li data-list-item-id="ee69cea1ac6cc3f466c001fbbd87973e5"><strong>View Character Info -&nbsp;</strong>Deposit or withdraw ATLAS, SOL, or ZINK.</li><li data-list-item-id="ecbe2102cf4871bac0ecae229fbb8c9df"><strong>Change Character -&nbsp;</strong>Create or switch between characters.</li><li data-list-item-id="e7b80ace3fd41c4b94824946335199b29"><strong>Help &amp; Support -&nbsp;</strong>Access reporting tools and support resources.</li><li data-list-item-id="e0e6414b77daa4c9c57cb0a181c749f8b"><strong>Disconnect Wallet -&nbsp;</strong>Sign your wallet out of the game.</li><li data-list-item-id="e709325c1eb34cca1b94e0e7212e1db91"><strong>Import Keypair -&nbsp;</strong>Restore a saved PTR account using a keypair file.</li><li data-list-item-id="e8544ab26579be3ed4b49cee868d1bb80"><strong>Export Keypair -&nbsp;</strong>Save your PTR account as a keypair file so you can import it later or use it on another device.</li><li data-list-item-id="eb69f2d641e5846d9583719dd732e2ce7"><strong>Command Settings -&nbsp;</strong>Adjust basic audio and visual settings.</li></ul><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 804/832;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52244580817171" width="804" height="832"></figure><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4JVDATSJH77A1X8QH26E3G">What to do next</h2><p>Once you understand the main menus, you can start using them to manage your activity in C4 PTR.</p><p>Recommended next steps:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id="ee24e0e1d738ac8b8a8db24016fcf3880">Learn how to use the C4 PTR map.</li><li data-list-item-id="ea5bf94e3b9a2d6f5945e382cef9285b4">Import your starting assets.</li><li data-list-item-id="e3131a34f6be043e5b35c398e0da3c25b">Create and manage fleets.</li><li data-list-item-id="e72c0e88790474a09b2d052dd5edbec84">Set up Claim Stakes.</li><li data-list-item-id="ee5a6fd63f527e1bae0288773654e3290">Report bugs or feedback through the support menu when needed.</li></ul></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

